data.title: International Journal of Integrated Care
data.meta_description: The International Journal of Integrated Care (IJIC) is an online, open-access, peer-reviewed scientific journal that publishes original articles in the field of integrated care on a continuous basis. IJIC has an Impact Factor of 2.60 (2023 JCR, received in June 2024) The IJIC 20th Anniversary Issue was published in 2021.
